<concept id="conceptId">
    <title>About Workspace Window</title>
    <conbody>
        <p>The <wintitle>Workspace</wintitle> window appears upon startup of <i>Phon</i>. To open
            this window if it has been closed, select the <menucascade>
                <uicontrol>Workspace</uicontrol>
                <uicontrol>Show Workspace window...</uicontrol>
            </menucascade> menu item.</p>
        <image placement="break" scale="40"
            href="../../images/AboutWorkspaceWindow.png" id="image_wdr_vlm_sc"/>
